caps.merge(options);

7ï¸âƒ£ Run Grid as a Service (Optional but Recommended)

Create service file:

sudo nano /etc/systemd/system/selenium-grid.service

[Unit]
Description=Selenium Grid
After=network.target

[Service]
ExecStart=/usr/bin/java -jar /opt/selenium/selenium-server.jar standalone
Restart=always
User=ubuntu

[Install]
WantedBy=multi-user.target

sudo systemctl daemon-reexec
sudo systemctl enable selenium-grid
sudo systemctl start selenium-grid

